3#ifndef __NVKM_DISP_OUTP_H__
4#define __NVKM_DISP_OUTP_H__
5#include <engine/disp.h>

7#include <subdev/bios.h>
8#include <subdev/bios/dcb.h>

10struct nvkm_output {
11 const struct nvkm_output_func *func;
12 struct nvkm_disp *disp;
13 int index;
14 struct dcb_output info;
15
16 // whatever (if anything) is pointed at by the dcb device entry
17 struct nvkm_i2c_bus *i2c;
18 int or;
19
20 struct list_head head;
21 struct nvkm_connector *conn;
22};
23
24struct nvkm_output_func {
25 void *(*dtor)(struct nvkm_output *);
26 void (*init)(struct nvkm_output *);
27 void (*fini)(struct nvkm_output *);
28};
29
30void nvkm_output_ctor(const struct nvkm_output_func *, struct nvkm_disp *,
31 int index, struct dcb_output *, struct nvkm_output *);
32int nvkm_output_new_(const struct nvkm_output_func *, struct nvkm_disp *,
33 int index, struct dcb_output *, struct nvkm_output **);
34void nvkm_output_del(struct nvkm_output **);
35void nvkm_output_init(struct nvkm_output *);
36void nvkm_output_fini(struct nvkm_output *);
37
38int nv50_dac_output_new(struct nvkm_disp *, int, struct dcb_output *,
39 struct nvkm_output **);
40int nv50_sor_output_new(struct nvkm_disp *, int, struct dcb_output *,
41 struct nvkm_output **);
42int nv50_pior_output_new(struct nvkm_disp *, int, struct dcb_output *,
43 struct nvkm_output **);
44
45u32 g94_sor_dp_lane_map(struct nvkm_device *, u8 lane);
46
47void gm204_sor_magic(struct nvkm_output *outp);

49#define OUTP_MSG(o,l,f,a...) do { \
50 struct nvkm_output *_outp = (o); \
51 nvkm_##l(&_outp->disp->engine.subdev, "outp %02x:%04x:%04x: "f"\n", \
52 _outp->index, _outp->info.hasht, _outp->info.hashm, ##a); \
53} while(0)
54#define OUTP_ERR(o,f,a...) OUTP_MSG((o), error, f, ##a)
55#define OUTP_DBG(o,f,a...) OUTP_MSG((o), debug, f, ##a)
56#define OUTP_TRACE(o,f,a...) OUTP_MSG((o), trace, f, ##a)
57#endif
